// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2026-1730 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: f24545c7-2504-522b-a2ba-41d2fbbf7d87

any where
  (process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:12.04*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:14.04*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:15.04*")
